 />\n後尾醫生講鼻膜薄<br />\n一唔噴藥唔洗訓 住香港有鼻敏感真係好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebcbba0949fe0655885a914c76385d6ac39412a1","tid":341454,"uid":55210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T19:09:28.000Z","msg":"咁多年黎因為鼻塞冇教好訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ab4a221afd1478700b25faab636e22371fc542e","tid":341454,"uid":16480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T19:13:44.000Z","msg":"我都係每日都鼻塞 之前問過醫生可以點解決<br />\n佢叫我移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52083ca04801d321684a6d991a33c38b6527838b","tid":341454,"uid":55210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T19:15:17.000Z","msg":"你哋有冇搞到個嘴唇好乾成日乾到流血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"674630fe2d50feb23495a25a018533a404a41ce0","tid":341454,"uid":96511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T19:17:36.000Z","msg":"樓豬平時有冇鼻敏感？"},{"pid":"5f81c65a046d00678e36ad15dea08fb1cbaba705","tid":341454,"uid":55210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T19:19:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓豬平時有冇鼻敏感？</blockquote><br />\n鼻敏感嘅定義係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由細到大個鼻都好多鼻水<br />\n夏天都要帶定紙巾抹鼻涕<br />\n唔知咁樣關唔關事<br />\n但係個人覺得瞓覺鼻塞係因為個鼻窿好細，入便好似有嘢塞住左咁"},{"pid":"b669f19341d0420594c2b8ed7f04e5f8bc4367ac","tid":341454,"uid":118827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T19:20:51.000Z","msg":"數數下細個塞到而家都10幾年,<br />\n薄荷膏冇乜用,<br />\n<br />\n反而食極薄荷,藍色個隻香口膠會通撚哂<br />\n<br />\n建議怕辣都要食"},{"pid":"62d4c797afe1a51bbfb8c4291cf2a15ccba0d5f7","tid":341454,"uid":55210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T19:21:00.000Z","msg":"用過燈照過嚟<br />\n 入邊好似有舊肉塞住左"},{"pid":"d3eca293432364ce292d18c0ccfcfa1f9ec8c03f","tid":341454,"uid":55210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T19:21:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>數數下細個塞到而家都10幾年,<br />\n薄荷膏冇乜用,<br />\n<br />\n反而食極薄荷,藍色個隻香口膠會通撚哂<br />\n<br />\n建議怕辣都要食</blockquote><br />\n你嘴唇會唔會好乾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"923a86c8cdd15c5480098f0df82c135e3d85fbff","tid":341454,"uid":96511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T19:24:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓豬平時有冇鼻敏感？</blockquote><br />\n鼻敏感嘅定義係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由細到大個鼻都好多鼻水<br />\n夏天都要帶定紙巾抹鼻涕<br />\n唔知咁樣關唔關事<br />\n但係個人覺得瞓覺鼻塞係因為個鼻窿好細，入便好似有嘢塞住左咁</blockquote><br />\n姐係會唔會有致敏源 例如塵個d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我都有鼻敏感 係冷氣房會勁d <br />\n所以夏天好濕滯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab0a968429ed8295ca056c562bc14e5ac58a2f01","tid":341454,"uid":118827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T19:25:05.000Z","msg":"唔知係咪大左鼻竇大d,冇以前咁塞,不過夜晚訓教都係要用口抖氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想問你地個鼻高唔高,有種感覺係鼻高就鼻腔窄,易d鼻塞咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時會因為個鼻吸氣量少,唔夠氧就好眼訓,要有意識地深呼吸幾次"},{"pid":"36a46bd8fef7f6847b435a78a862730105979da3","tid":341454,"uid":118827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T19:25:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係每日都鼻塞 之前問過醫生可以點解決<br />\n佢叫我移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"139d200de24e7698fabca253b1cd5dbc68f57546","tid":341454,"uid":118827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T19:26:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你哋有冇搞到個嘴唇好乾成日乾到流血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n會,經常性乾到甩皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過我少飲水"},{"pid":"ce26dd90655451e72d31fef401f9ce0ad60b9f15","tid":341454,"uid":55210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T19:26:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓豬平時有冇鼻敏感？</blockquote><br />\n鼻敏感嘅定義係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由細到大個鼻都好多鼻水<br />\n夏天都要帶定紙巾抹鼻涕<br />\n唔知咁樣關唔關事<br />\n但係個人覺得瞓覺鼻塞係因為個鼻窿好細，入便好似有嘢塞住左咁</blockquote><br />\n姐係會唔會有致敏源 例如塵個d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我都有鼻敏感 係冷氣房會勁d <br />\n所以夏天好濕滯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n麈會搞到我成日打乞嗤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"259822d98fa1430092cd4b28cb3919d800d4cdac","tid":341454,"uid":118827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T19:28:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓豬平時有冇鼻敏感？</blockquote><br />\n鼻敏感嘅定義係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由細到大個鼻都好多鼻水<br />\n夏天都要帶定紙巾抹鼻涕<br />\n唔知咁樣關唔關事<br />\n但係個人覺得瞓覺鼻塞係因為個鼻窿好細，入便好似有嘢塞住左咁</blockquote><br />\n姐係會唔會有致敏源 例如塵個d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我都有鼻敏感 係冷氣房會勁d <br />\n所以夏天好濕滯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nme2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇紙巾會死..d鼻涕多到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}